ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 274, New Brunswick
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER No. 274 in order to (1) declare the natural disaster to be of concern to the federal government; and (2) authorize the provision of financial assistance to New Brunswick with respect to the rainstorm that occurred from December 18 to December 19, 2023.
